## What is eternity?

Eternity is the now famous, but not yet implemented, ORM framework for Nit.

### Required features

* Easy to use frontend
* Pluggable backend (SQLite, Mongo etc...)
* Out of the box basic CRUD operations
* Possibility to redefine out of the box behaviour
* Select with table jointures

## Coding party objectives

* Define good use-cases for Eternity
* Write Eternity specifications and base conception from use-cases
* Implement Eternity specifications
* Write Eternity documentation

